<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3764073>
    dc:description "FIGURE 1. Physalaemus claptoni sp. nov. (holotype UFMG 16784; adult male, SVL 17.3 mm): (A) dorsal and (B) ventral views. Scale bar=5 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3764073/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3764078>
    dc:description "FIGURE 3. Physalaemus claptoni sp. nov. (holotype UFMG 16784). Live adult male from Serra do Cipó, Municipality of Santana do Riacho, Minas Gerais, Brazil." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3764078/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3764080>
    dc:description "FIGURE 4. Color pattern variation of Physalaemus claptoni sp. nov. in live paratypes specimens. Photos not to scale." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3764080/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3764084>
    dc:description "FIGURE 6. Physalaemus claptoni sp. nov. (paratype UFMG 16775; adult female, SVL 18.2 mm): (A) dorsal and (B) ventral views. Scale bar=5 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3764084/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3764082>
    dc:description "FIGURE 5. Ventral color pattern of Physalaemus claptoni sp. nov. in a live paratype specimen." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3764082/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3764086>
    dc:description "FIGURE 7. Nuptial pads of (A) Physalaemus claptoni sp. nov. (paratype UFMG 5418), brown, not divided and (B) Physalaemus rupestris (topotype UFMG 13369), white cream, divided. Scale bar=5 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3764086/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3764075>
    dc:description "FIGURE 2. Physalaemus claptoni sp. nov. (holotype UFMG 16784; adult male): (A) dorsal and (B) lateral views of head, (C) ventral views of right hand and (D) right foot. Scale bar=2 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3764075/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3764088>
    dc:description "FIGURE 8. Advertisement call of (A, B) Physalaemus claptoni sp. nov. and (C, D) P. rupestris. (A) Spectrogram (above) and oscillogram (below) of a single call composed of note A and B; (B) spectrogram of six calls in sequence. Observe that the second call of the call sequence, note A was released alone, without the note B. Recordings CBUFMG 749, paratype (Audio S1). (C) Spectrogram (above) and oscillogram (below) of a single call composed of note A and B; (D) oscillogram of 12 calls in sequence, nine composed of A + B notes released in sequence and three composed of note A emitted solely between A + B note calls. Recordings CBUFMG 754, topotype (Audio S2)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3764088/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3764090>
    dc:description "FIGURE 9. Physalaemus rupestris (UFMG 13369; adult male): (A) dorsal and (B) ventral views. Scale bar=5 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3764090/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3764092>
    dc:description "FIGURE 10. Phylogenetic relationships of Physalaemus claptoni sp. nov. inferred from the H1 fragment matrix using maximum parsimony criterion. Numbers above branches indicate bootstrap values (%). Only bootstrap values greater than 50% are shown." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3764092/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3764094>
    dc:description "FIGURE 11. Geographic distribution of Physalaemus claptoni sp. nov. and of the other species of the P. deimaticus species group. Triangles refers to species type localities. Abbreviations: MG=State of Minas Gerais, ES=State of Espírito Santo, RJ=State of Rio de Janeiro, SP=State of São Paulo." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3764094/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

